nodes.text: The Jungle battle droid, also known as the Kashyyyk Battle Droid, was a variant of the B1-series battle droid used by the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars. They had camouflage markings that resembled green plants. Their markings were similar to the AAT Driver Battle Droid.
The Jungle battle droid first appeared in Star Wars Battlefront II, a 2017 video game created by Electronic Arts.
